---
layout: layouts/base.njk
title: Music
description: "Stream and download Jay Trainer's complete discography — eight releases of folk, acoustic rock, and Americana from Pittsburgh, Pennsylvania. From The Waking Hours to A Whisper of Ruin."
permalink: /music/
---

<div class="listing-header">
  <img src="/assets/images/steel-texture.png" alt="" class="listing-header-bg" loading="eager">
  <div class="section-label">Discography</div>
  <h1 class="section-title">The <em>Music</em></h1>
  <div class="divider"></div>
  <p class="listing-intro">
    Eight releases spanning nearly two decades — from the earliest live recordings to the expanded deluxe edition. Every record is a chapter. Start anywhere.
  </p>
</div>

<div class="listing-content">
  {# Featured Release #}
  {% set featured = releases | findBySlug("a-whisper-of-ruin-deluxe") %}
  {% if featured %}
  <div class="featured-release reveal">
    <div class="featured-image-wrap">
      <a href="/music/{{ featured.slug }}/">
        <img src="{{ featured.coverArt }}" alt="{{ featured.title }}" loading="lazy">
      </a>
    </div>
    <div class="featured-content">
      <div class="featured-tag">Latest Album — {{ featured.year }}</div>
      <h3 class="featured-title">A Whisper Of <em>Ruin</em><br>— Deluxe Edition</h3>
      <p class="featured-desc">{{ featured.description }}</p>
      <div class="featured-tracklist">
        <ol>
          {% for track in featured.tracks %}
          <li><span>{{ track.title }}</span><span>{{ track.duration }}</span></li>
          {% endfor %}
        </ol>
      </div>
      <div class="featured-btns">
        <a href="/music/{{ featured.slug }}/" class="btn-primary">Stream & Download</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  {% endif %}

  <div class="music-grid">
    {% for r in releases %}
      {% if not r.featured %}
        {% include "partials/music-card.njk" %}
      {% endif %}
    {% endfor %}
  </div>
</div>

{% include "partials/streaming-banner.njk" %}
